Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:44.77,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,痛 痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.37,0:01:47.37,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,擦伤 幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.34,0:01:49.04,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.18,0:01:51.43,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:01:56.21,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,回答 请求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.91,0:02:01.87,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,讨厌 这岛怎么回事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:11.28,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,嘉依卡掉哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:23.00,Default,David,0,0,0,,没受伤吧 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:24.29,Default,Red,0,0,0,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:27.21,Default,David,0,0,0,,看来咱飘到要找的岛了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:30.83,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,那团雾 应该是魔法做出来隐藏小岛的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:33.42,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:34.12,Default,Red,0,0,0,,负伤？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:38.05,Default,David,0,0,0,,嗯 被船的碎片伤到了 真倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:42.30,Default,David,0,0,0,,快点上岛吧 免得刚才那怪物回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:01.07,Default,David,0,0,0,,在担心乱破师小哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:02.60,Default,Red,0,0,0,,否…否定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:05.90,Default,David,0,0,0,,不用担心 这点小事他死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:14.42,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,这情况下魔法还真方便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:16.32,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:20.55,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,要不是兄长跟嘉依卡吵架 这会儿应该已经到顶了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:22.47,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,这是在挖苦我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:25.06,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,我怎么会挖苦敬爱的兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:30.14,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,不过 如果兄长有被言语侮辱的性癖 我乐意效劳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:31.64,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,闭嘴快爬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:45.13,Default,Orthros,0,0,0,,Herukerun... Unzerun... Korukerun... Peie... Sebue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:54.33,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,双头犬…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:56.81,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,Els, nyme, ainkt, mu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:03:59.71,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,显现吧 光煌之物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:01.22,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,【闪耀者】
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:27.78,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,入侵者 逮捕 带走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:30.69,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,这座岛 居民？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:34.19,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我 这座岛知道 请求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:37.45,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,入侵者 逮捕 带走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:45.30,Default,David,0,0,0,,岛是找到了 可之后该干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:47.97,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,奇伊说来了就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:53.43,Default,Red,0,0,0,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:58.13,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,这玩意…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:04:59.66,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,是嘉依卡的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:02.15,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,看来确实来这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:04.05,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:04.65,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:11.95,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,亚人兵…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:14.22,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,他们是这岛的警卫？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.22,0:05:15.14,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,像是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:18.92,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,他们会在这里晃悠 证明肯定有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:23.47,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,如果嘉依卡也在这 可能已经被他们抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:28.11,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,我去跟踪他们 阿卡莉在树林里找找
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:28.93,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:38.63,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,岛的地下 巨大设施
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:42.09,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,父亲的遗产 存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:52.84,Default,Wizard,0,0,0,,伊茨玛希大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:55.54,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,弃兽们干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:06:00.64,Default,Wizard,0,0,0,,是 目前正与亚人兵部队合作 搜寻入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:02.73,Default,Wizard,0,0,0,,应该很快会有报告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:12.89,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,观察过程和记录数据
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:15.88,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,这种事有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:19.84,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,陛下所求之物早已完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:25.90,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,但是 知道如何启动它的 只有贾兹皇帝陛下一人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:28.92,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,我们连线索都没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:31.72,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,朕命不久矣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:37.49,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,陛下如今已驾崩 这座岛还有意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:40.28,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:44.40,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,搜索队回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:49.21,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,入侵小岛的几人已抓获 关进地牢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:52.65,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,应该是从附近经过的货船上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:54.69,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,要立刻审问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:56.01,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,不急
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:07:00.62,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,另外 南侧悬崖处也有入侵者的踪迹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:03.58,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,附近搜索过后 没发现可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:06.19,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,搜查已暂时中止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:07.60,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,中止？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过上岛的人要全部抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:12.82,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:16.26,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,但是报告上说 光线太暗路况也很差
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:18.33,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,深追下去搜索队也会有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:20.56,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,少跟我顶嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:26.52,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,是我打发慈悲 启用你们这些走投无路的战争的遗留品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:29.71,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,你们这些亚人按吩咐办事就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:33.84,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:36.86,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,嗯 区区亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:39.70,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,量产型数量已成规模
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:43.54,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,小心我拿你们当实验材料处理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:53.96,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:55.48,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:07:58.70,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我拘捕 为何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:01.45,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,这座岛 秘密 目的 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:04.53,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,我什么都不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:08.34,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,上头的人早晚会来 到时去问他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.74,0:08:09.70,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:12.86,Default,Wizard,0,0,0,,娥苏拉 弃兽怎么还没喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:14.04,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:14.78,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,娥苏拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:18.26,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,娥苏拉 高洁之花？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:20.54,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,嗯 是拉克语
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:22.74,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,你懂拉克语？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:25.45,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯 出身 贾兹帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:26.21,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,你也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:27.06,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:27.79,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:31.29,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,这座岛 研究 贾兹皇帝的命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:36.38,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,抱歉 详细情况我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:07.17,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,把整座岛挖空造出来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.57,0:09:08.96,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,好大的手笔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:23.80,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,又是弃兽？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:35.48,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.23,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,阿卡莉来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:39.76,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,芙蕾多妮卡 嘉依卡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:42.45,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,诶 我也在找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:43.87,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:46.49,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事……这座岛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.41,0:09:56.38,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:58.88,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,就你一个？芙蕾多妮卡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:00.69,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,走散
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:01.59,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,先从这里出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.46,0:10:06.47,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,有没有人来 帮我看着点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:09.09,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托鲁 谢罪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:13.96,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我 不听劝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:15.15,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,大家 麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:16.58,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:19.49,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,不 我也太急功近利了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:22.19,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,再说岛也找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:24.20,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,总之 这事回头再说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.87,0:10:26.82,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,这岛肯定有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.22,0:10:28.37,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,棺材和机枪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:30.38,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,棺材 芙蕾多妮卡拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.78,0:10:31.58,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,机枪已没收
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.87,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,机枪先不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:37.89,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,先逃到个安全的地方 再考虑之后的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:38.96,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:47.89,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,装铠龙和双头犬？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:48.77,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:51.47,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,袭击船的是大海魔…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:54.67,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,这岛上的人 驯养着弃兽？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.39,0:11:00.92,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,这边不太妙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:02.50,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,找别的出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.90,0:11:03.32,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:18.25,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:29.93,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,潜下去应该连着外面的大海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:32.93,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,但根本看不出有多深啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:40.65,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,弃兽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:44.86,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,那不是自然的弃兽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:45.97,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:51.62,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,它们都是复制品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.30,0:12:11.49,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,大海魔…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:22.03,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,刚才是它在说话？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:23.82,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,它能说话？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:27.66,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,大海魔 高智能 等同装铠龙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:29.57,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,复制品是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:37.20,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,这设施中 在研究如何用炼生魔法量产弃兽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:41.01,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,扔在这里的 就是其失败品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:43.72,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,你也是其中之一？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:46.72,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,我是被抓来做实验的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:51.10,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,通过研究我的肉体 进行复制
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.13,0:12:54.52,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,诞生了量产型大海魔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:59.19,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,待遇 残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:02.50,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,银色头发 紫色瞳孔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:05.57,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,背棺材的公主 嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:08.27,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,你认识嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:12.08,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,我曾遇到过一个自称嘉依卡的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:16.79,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,她知道了自己的命运 抛弃了嘉依卡之名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:21.13,Default,Layla,0,0,0,,但某一天 我得知了真相
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.98,0:13:25.75,Default,Layla,0,0,0,,一切只是为收集《遗体》的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:28.05,Default,Layla,0,0,0,,嘉依卡是 帮助嘉依卡的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:30.09,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,蕾拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:31.95,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,她来过这座岛？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:33.93,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我 真相 追寻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:35.56,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 真相 知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:39.34,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,我的生命即将消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:44.89,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,你的问题我会如数作答 背棺材的公主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:48.07,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我 什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:50.56,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,推动命运的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:56.22,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,带着棺材 收集遗体 将自身化为道具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:58.37,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,以开启命运之锁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:00.65,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,命运？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:04.84,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,我来收餐具时 发现门开着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:07.21,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,有同伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:09.63,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,估计是搜索队漏掉的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:12.32,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,对不起 基里尔 是我一时疏忽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:13.80,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,这不怪娥苏拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:16.77,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,但是 肯定会受罚的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:19.95,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,因为伊茨玛希大人讨厌我们亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:21.29,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,没准会是死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:22.56,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,这种事他休想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:24.71,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,我马上抓人回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:31.39,Default,David,0,0,0,,怎么 这匆忙劲有点怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:33.00,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,看来是出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:36.31,Default,David,0,0,0,,运气好的话 咱们没准也有机会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:39.16,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,喂 不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.43,0:14:46.90,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,人类所谓的魔法 是将思念具象化的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:49.94,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,遥远的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们弃兽 从人类诞生之前就与这力量为伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:59.56,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,后来人类诞生 开始向往魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:02.76,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,模仿研究我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,最终借助人工的魔法器具 施展出多彩的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:12.34,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,魔法器具 机枪？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:19.33,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,随后人类的魔法技术 因一位魔法师取得飞跃性发展
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:24.71,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,有<禁断皇帝>之称的男人 亚尔图·贾兹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:28.11,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.51,0:15:34.09,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,所谓嘉依卡 是贾兹皇帝用来实现胸中宏伟野心的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:38.12,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,他们的生与死 喜悦与哀伤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.52,0:15:42.75,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,都按既定的齿轮而动 无法反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:44.56,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,为什么 你知道这些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:51.84,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,从太古起我们就与其他个体思维想通 将一切看在眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:55.87,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,一旦命运迈出脚步 不止是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:16:01.20,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,我们弃兽以及其他的生命都将会被卷入破坏与杀戮的漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:04.91,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,嘉依卡手握这柄钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:07.40,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,这一点万不可忘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:13.11,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.98,0:16:16.63,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 别离我太远
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:17.09,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:25.39,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,别放跑他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:38.78,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:41.74,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.97,0:16:46.03,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.43,0:16:46.71,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:47.69,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:50.13,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,你刚才叫她嘉依卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:52.59,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,你是嘉依卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.71,0:16:55.34,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,嘉依卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:57.28,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:17:01.57,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,确认之后 发现抓到的另一组入侵者之后也有个相似的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:03.77,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,那边也自称嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:06.62,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,两个嘉依卡同时来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:08.69,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,这是偶然吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:11.03,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,不 很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:14.15,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,带到这里来 两个一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:17.48,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,城堡？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:20.97,Default,Drunk,0,0,0,,没错 飘在天上的大城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:25.33,Default,Drunk,0,0,0,,站在前面山丘上 能很清楚看到国界附近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:29.29,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,在贾兹帝国国界附近 看到天上飞的城堡了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:30.29,Default,Drunk,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:35.28,Default,Drunk,0,0,0,,在月光下 那么大个的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:39.26,Default,Drunk,0,0,0,,还一次出来五六个 给我都吓傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.07,0:17:41.33,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,五六个？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:45.12,Default,Drunk,0,0,0,,而且到了早晨 就像烟一样消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:46.52,Default,Zita,0,0,0,,什么时候的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:48.89,Default,Drunk,0,0,0,,是我还小的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:52.38,Default,Drunk,0,0,0,,80年…不 90年前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:53.18,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:56.56,Default,Zita,0,0,0,,是什么形状 能画在这上面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:01.81,Default,Zita,0,0,0,,看着像航天要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:04.16,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,贾兹帝国里飘着航天要塞？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:09.34,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,绕道国界附近 本想找找遗产的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:11.62,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,结果听到个怪事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:16.74,Default,Matheus,0,0,0,,但是 那个时代应该还没发明出航天要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.14,0:18:19.88,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,跟皇帝的遗产貌似没什么关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:22.88,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,不好下结论
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:26.95,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,遗产 航天要塞 还有嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:31.10,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,贾兹皇帝究竟想留下什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:34.91,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,伊茨玛希大人 带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:49.37,Default,Red,0,0,0,,接触 拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:51.08,Default,Red,0,0,0,,无礼之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:52.83,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,又见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.44,0:19:01.73,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:04.61,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,并排一站果然很相像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:07.20,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,欢迎 嘉依卡·贾兹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:11.85,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,我是贾兹帝国魔法技术员副院长 维克多·伊茨玛希
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:14.93,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,魔法技术院？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.33,0:19:16.10,Default,Niva,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:18.19,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,有反应了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.61,0:19:20.48,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.15,0:19:22.21,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,啊 我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:25.78,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,上次嘉依卡来时还在开发之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:27.82,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,那么果然嘉依卡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:28.78,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,上次？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:29.91,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,蕾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:33.62,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,太棒了 收获超出预期
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:37.96,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,你们来这里也在贾兹皇帝计划之中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:41.31,Default,Red,0,0,0,,你 父亲的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:42.92,Default,Red,0,0,0,,我 皇帝的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:45.23,Default,Red,0,0,0,,捆缚 监禁 无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:52.40,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,女儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:53.85,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,听好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.70,0:19:57.35,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,贾兹皇帝可没有女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:19:59.86,Default,Red,0,0,0,,一…一派胡言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:05.11,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,战后 街头巷尾满是战争孤儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.15,0:20:12.29,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,计划书中写道【从其中秘选一批同龄女孩】
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:15.36,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,【对记忆进行了魔法处理】
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:26.54,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,在所有女孩脑中 加入了同一份贾兹皇帝女儿的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:30.43,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,这就是嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:37.73,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,觉醒的嘉依卡会准备好棺材 开始收集皇帝陛下的遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:43.07,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,不过收集的理由会因个体不同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:47.49,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,就是它 证据不就在这吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:50.03,Default,Red,0,0,0,,否定 否定 否定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:56.92,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,所谓嘉依卡 是贾兹皇帝用来实现胸中宏伟野心的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:21:01.79,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,他们的生与死 喜悦与哀伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:06.38,Default,Kraken,0,0,0,,都按既定的齿轮而动 无法反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:08.37,Default,Layla,0,0,0,,你还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.77,0:21:13.00,Default,Layla,0,0,0,,自己为何而活 因何而生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:18.64,Default,Layla,0,0,0,,当知道这些时 你会从心底绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.89,0:21:21.15,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:26.36,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,捏造的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:28.94,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,真是来得太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.34,0:21:31.32,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,这下研究也会大幅进展
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.49,0:21:35.99,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,我取出你们一部分大脑进行分析
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:39.41,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,混蛋 开什么玩笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.81,0:21:42.06,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,别激动 不用担心
